  "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nThere is big reorg on Goerli at slot https://goerli.beaconcha.in/slot/6172162\r\n\r\n```\r\n1912099:Jul-28 19:51:49.645[chain]         verbose: New chain head slot=6172159, root=0xb62d724b832fcb588ff6f590f39953337744cd1a85a4b3818ec1694deeff0c8f, delaySec=1.6449999809265137\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n1913209:Jul-28 19:52:29.981[chain]         verbose: New chain head slot=6172162, root=0x3a33c88767a5bfaf8cdbcd3f3e63c5eb1d913e5ca7c6f4b1e314b9440e5ba865, delaySec=5.980999946594238\r\n```\r\n\r\ntheir common ancestor is slot 6172126\r\n\r\nBlock parent distance metric was able to catch it\r\n<img width=\"806\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-29 at 15 11 49\" src=\"https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/assets/10568965/fa2c5df0-3a21-4195-b369-0217b82fb38b\">\r\n\r\nhowever \"Reorg depth\" was not\r\n<img width=\"783\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-29 at 15 12 30\" src=\"https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/assets/10568965/1736cb78-1814-4e17-b2b8-25191527881a\">\r\n\r\nI also wasn't able to find \"Chain reorg\" log https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/v1.9.2/packages/beacon-node/src/chain/blocks/importBlock.ts#L262\r\n\r\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nShould emit chain reorg event with depth 36\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n_No response_\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_\n\n### Operating system\n\nLinux\n\n### Lodestar version or commit hash\n\nv1.9.2",
